Version 1.5.1   27 Sep 2013

    * Tweak the help documentation and README to be clearer about defaults.

Version 1.5.0   27 Sep 2013

    * Allow thread lifetimes up to 5 hours.
    * Update the event database while the thread is running, instead of when it finishes.
    * Add a help screen with some basic instructions.
    * Initial release to Google code.

Version 0.0.0   15 Sep 2013

    * First "public" release of code to Google Code repository
